    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>图千秋是一款以拼图为基础的、充满欢乐和自由气息的游戏，您将在游戏中解锁众多“超”能力，快速领略“拼”图乐趣。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/3cf7da5d6d4f15f7490b6e3770b47ca2.poster.avif?t=1771119953\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/3cf7da5d6d4f15f7490b6e3770b47ca2.webm?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/3cf7da5d6d4f15f7490b6e3770b47ca2.mp4?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢乐向</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将传统的拼图玩法与独特的能力机制相结合，让您可以打造不同的增效策略，挑战目标时间，快速完成拼图以获得更多奖励！游戏场景中还有意想不到的事件和惊喜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/a582d75ea21bf69f09ae20afb687fa2f.poster.avif?t=1771119953\" width=616 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/a582d75ea21bf69f09ae20afb687fa2f.webm?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/a582d75ea21bf69f09ae20afb687fa2f.mp4?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心拼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>图千秋</strong>，您拥有随心所欲的自由：想拼就拼，随时保存；想拼什么就拼什么，随心载入自己想拼的图片，只要用游戏内奖励就能解锁；想怎么拼就怎么拼，随意搭配多种能力，开发属于自己的玩法。此外，游戏中还有多种主题色彩供您自由选择。有了这款游戏，就等于拥有了万千拼图和无限可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/820a3d8f2673bc0170aafa8e63987f2a.poster.avif?t=1771119953\" width=616 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/820a3d8f2673bc0170aafa8e63987f2a.webm?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/820a3d8f2673bc0170aafa8e63987f2a.mp4?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >花样玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从生命萌芽到未来社区，从广袤天地到浩瀚星宇，从累累硕果到原初之爱……拼图多多、玩法多多，20多种能力，数百种组合，打破传统拼图的界限，正等您亲自体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/97f7db1790b36c9cbac52ecdba25773a.poster.avif?t=1771119953\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/97f7db1790b36c9cbac52ecdba25773a.webm?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/97f7db1790b36c9cbac52ecdba25773a.mp4?t=1771119953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>图千秋</u></strong><u>，不仅是拼图，更是一段探索发现的旅程。</u></p>",
